<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Ending With -AGE — Scrabble Suffix Scoring Guide</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The -AGE suffix turns verbs into nouns (block→blockage, pass→passage) and creates some of Scrabble's most satisfying extension plays. While -AGE itself adds only 4 base points, the words it forms often contain high-value consonants like K, W, and CK combinations that push scores into the 20+ range.</p>

<p>Mastering -AGE words gives you reliable extension plays and defensive options that shut down board sections effectively.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why -AGE Matters in Scrabble</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">A(1)+G(2)+E(1) base</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">200+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid -AGE words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">3–12</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The G tile adds 2 points and creates strong consonant clusters. Words like WRECKAGE and BLOCKAGE pair -AGE with the CK combo (C=3, K=5) for instant high scores. The suffix is also defensive — longer -AGE words are hard to extend further.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring -AGE Words</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
